rk=Gândul |author=Andrei Luca Popescu |date=2015-11-03 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912060455/https://www.gandul.info/tragedia-din-clubul-colectiv/zeci-de-mii-de-romani-le-au-cerut-demisia-lui-ponta-oprea-si-piedone-cateva-zile-s-au-ascuns-miercuri-au-demisionat-dar-protestele-au-continuat-14871561 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和批评未经消防部门批准向夜总会颁发营业执照的第四区区长{{le|克里斯蒂安·安波佩斯库·佩多|Cristian Popescu Piedone}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stiri.tvr.ro/primarul-piedone-acuzat-ca-nu-trebuia-sa-dea-autorizatie-clubului-colectiv-pe-baza-declaratiei-pe-p_67043.html |title=Primarul Piedone, acuzat că nu trebuia să dea autorizaţie clubului Colectiv pe baza declaraţiei pe proprie răspundere |work=Ştirile TVR |date=2015-11-02 |access-date=2015-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107061812/http://stiri.tvr.ro/primarul-piedone-acuzat-ca-nu-trebuia-sa-dea-autorizatie-clubului-colectiv-pe-baza-declaratiei-pe-p_67043.html |archive-date=2015-11-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在政府大楼前，宪法用重卡作路障以组织示威者向大楼挺进<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediafax.ro/social/tragedia-din-clubul-colectiv-peste-10-000-de-manifestanti-in-piata-victoriei-ei-striga-demisia-live-text-foto-14872541 |title=TRAGEDIA din clubul Colectiv: Peste 10.000 de manifestanți în Piaţa Victoriei. Ei strigă: "Demisia!" |work=Mediafax |date=2015-11-03 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106022743/http://www.mediafax.ro/social/tragedia-din-clubul-colectiv-peste-10-000-de-manifestanti-in-piata-victoriei-ei-striga-demisia-live-text-foto-14872541 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在胜利广场，示威者游行到内政部，跪在地上举行默哀仪式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-11-03/thousands-protest-against-romanian-premier-after-32-die-in-fire |title=Thousands Protest Against Romanian Premier After 32 Die in Fire |work=Bloomberg |author=Andra Timu, Irina Vilcu |date=2015-11-03 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106151348/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-11-03/thousands-protest-against-romanian-premier-after-32-die-in-fire |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他们高喊“不要脸”和“刺客”，打出“腐败屠杀”的标语。到当地时间晚上10点，28000-30000人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.realitatea.net/protest-in-capitala-dupa-tragedia-colectiv-32-000-de-oameni-au-iesit-in-strada-demisia-live_1822557.html |title=Protest în Capitală, după tragedia COLECTIV.32.000 de oameni cer DEMISIA lui Ponta, Oprea şi Piedone |work=Realitatea.net |date=2015-11-03 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151108012700/http://www.realitatea.net/protest-in-capitala-dupa-tragedia-colectiv-32-000-de-oameni-au-iesit-in-strada-demisia-live_1822557.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（一说估计超过35000人）来到现正广场，其中有示威者拆除[[罗马尼亚人民宫|议会宫殿]]周围的栅栏。[[布拉索夫|布拉索夫]]、[[普洛耶什蒂|普洛耶什蒂]]和[[雅西|雅西]]等地亦爆发示威。总统[[克劳斯·约翰尼斯|克劳斯·约翰尼斯]]欢迎街头示威，警告称政治阶层不能忽视这类事件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/peste-2000-de-oameni-sunt-in-strada-la-piata-universitatii-oamenii-cer-dreptate-pentru-victimele-din-colectiv.html |title=CORUPTIA UCIDE: "Nu aveti coloana, decat oficiala". 25.000 de oameni sunt in strada. Mesajul lui Klaus Iohannis |work=Stirile Pro TV |date=2015-11-03 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105222017/http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/peste-2000-de-oameni-sunt-in-strada-la-piata-universitatii-oamenii-cer-dreptate-pentru-victimele-din-colectiv.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

示威者还批评[[罗马尼亚正教会|罗马尼亚正教会]]及其领导者{{le|罗马尼亚元老丹尼尔|Patriarch Daniel of Romania|元老丹尼尔}}在夜总会大会后缺乏明显的反应。成千上万的示威者游行到教会所在的布加勒斯特市中心的{{le|都主教教区|Dealul Mitropoliei}}<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.romaniatv.net/live/mii-de-persoane-la-un-protest-in-capitala-manifestantii-au-blocat-piata-universitatii_254750.html | title=Tragedia din Colectiv. Peste 25.000 de persoane, în stradă. Au cerut demisia lui Piedone, Oprea şi Ponta  Citeste mai mult pe RTV.NET: http://www.romaniatv.net/mii-de-persoane-la-un-protest-in-capitala-manifestantii-au-blocat-piata-universitatii_254750.html#ixzz3qWVNzLhF | accessdate=2015-11-04 | archive-date=2015-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106020811/http://www.romaniatv.net/live/mii-de-persoane-la-un-protest-in-capitala-manifestantii-au-blocat-piata-universitatii_254750.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

11月4日早上，蓬塔政府辞职<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/04/us-romania-government-ponta-idUSKCN0ST0XR20151104 |title=Romanian PM Ponta quits after protests, paves way for cabinet reshuffle |work=Reuters |author=Radu-Sorin Marinas, Luiza Ilie |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107025733/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/04/us-romania-government-ponta-idUSKCN0ST0XR20151104 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/04/romanian-government-resigns-nightclub-fire-victor-ponta |title=Bucharest nightclub fire: Romania's PM and government resign after protests |work=The Guardian |author=Mark Tran |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107175840/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/04/romanian-government-resigns-nightclub-fire-victor-ponta |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/victor-ponta-resigns-live-romanian-prime-minister-quits-day-after-mass-protests-over-nightclub-fire-a6720486.html |title=Romanian Prime Minister Victor Ponta resigns the day after mass protests over nightclub fire |work=The Independent |author=Alexandra Sims |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106205753/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/victor-ponta-resigns-live-romanian-prime-minister-quits-day-after-mass-protests-over-nightclub-fire-a6720486.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但蓬塔自己仍保留代总理一职直至新政府形成<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Politica/VICTOR+PONTA+DEMISIONEAZA | title=VICTOR PONTA A DEMISIONAT | accessdate=2015-11-04 | archive-date=2015-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106204557/http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Politica/VICTOR+PONTA+DEMISIONEAZA | dead-url=no }}</ref>。蓬塔在声明中表示：“我希望政府的辞职能让走上街头的人们感到满意”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34720183 |title=Romania PM Ponta resigns over Bucharest nightclub fire |work=BBC News |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115091112/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34720183 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。安在蓬塔身上的压力在上个月已有显现。2015年10月，他税务欺诈丑闻把[[社会民主党_(罗马尼亚)|社会民主党]]的领导权丢给Liviu Dragnea，成为该国第一位因腐败出庭受审的现任总理<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.euronews.com/2015/11/04/romania-s-prime-minister-victor-ponta-to-resign-today-following-protests-over/ |title=Romania: PM Victor Ponta resigns |work=Euronews |author=Sarah Joanne Taylor |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106215822/http://www.euronews.com/2015/11/04/romania-s-prime-minister-victor-ponta-to-resign-today-following-protests-over/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。政府宣布辞职后一个小时，蓬塔宣布辞职<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mediafax.ro/social/primarul-cristian-popescu-piedone-demisioneaza-si-el-surse-14873457 | title=Primarul Cristian Popescu Piedone demisionează şi el - surse | accessdate=2015-11-04 | archive-date=2015-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106233018/http://www.mediafax.ro/social/primarul-cristian-popescu-piedone-demisioneaza-si-el-surse-14873457 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他接受了他在悲剧中所扮演角色，对他的行为和不作为表示遗憾，表示：“这是一次错误，我保证我没有在事发后第一天或第二天辞职后还继续做下去<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Politica/CRISTIAN+POPESCU+PIEDONE+A+DEMISIONAT |title=Cristian Popescu Piedone a demisionat: "E un act. Onoarea trebuia să fie în prima zi" |work=Digi24 |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106204515/http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Politica/CRISTIAN+POPESCU+PIEDONE+A+DEMISIONAT |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

同日，尽管蓬塔辞职，抗议活动还是继续进行到第二天晚上。在布加勒斯特，大约有3.5万名示威者<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Stiri/Oamenii+ies+din+nou+in+strada+in+Bucuresti+si+in+alte+orase | title=70.000 de români au ieşit în stradă. Oamenii au strigat: "Nu mă cumperi cu două demisii!" | accessdate=2015-11-04 | archive-date=2015-11-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106204806/http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Stiri/Oamenii+ies+din+nou+in+strada+in+Bucuresti+si+in+alte+orase | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/noi-proteste-sunt-anuntate-si-pentru-miercuri-seara-ce-vor-manifestantii-sa-se-intample-dupa-caderea-guvernului.html#2050 |title=CORUPTIA UCIDE: Peste 35.000 de oameni au ocupat strazile Capitalei. Proteste de amploare au avut loc in toata tara |work=Stirile Pro TV |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107013113/http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/noi-proteste-sunt-anuntate-si-pentru-miercuri-seara-ce-vor-manifestantii-sa-se-intample-dupa-caderea-guvernului.html#2050 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[蒂米什瓦拉|蒂米什瓦拉]]有1万名，[[雅西|雅西]]和[[克拉约瓦|克拉约瓦]]有5000名，[[克卢日-纳波卡|克卢日-纳波卡]]有4500名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.realitatea.net/proteste-masive-in-romania-70-000-de-oameni-in-strada-nu-doar-guvernul-jos-tot-sistemul_1823844.html?utm_source=Cub-Homepage&utm_medium=Clicks&utm_campaign=trkweb |title=Proteste masive în România. 70.000 de oameni, în stradă: "Nu doar Guvernul, jos tot Sistemul" |work=Realitatea.net |date=2015-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107222901/http://www.realitatea.net/proteste-masive-in-romania-70-000-de-oameni-in-strada-nu-doar-guvernul-jos-tot-sistemul_1823844.html?utm_source=Cub-Homepage&utm_medium=Clicks&utm_campaign=trkweb |archivedate=2015-11-07 |accessdate=2015-11-08 }}</ref>，[[锡比乌|锡比乌]]4000名，[[巴克乌|巴克乌]]、[[康斯坦察|康斯坦察]]和[[加拉茨|加拉茨]]3000人，[[福克沙尼|福克沙尼]]1000人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://adevarul.ro/news/eveniment/ce-nu-s-a-vazut-televizor-timpul-protestelor-bucuresti-s-a-incercat-deturnarea-manifestatiei-miting-anti-iohannis-1_563a9ee2f5eaafab2c4fc96a/index.html |title=Ce nu s-a văzut la televizor în timpul protestelor din Bucureşti: cum s-a încercat deturnarea manifestaţiei către un miting anti-Iohannis |work=Adevărul |author=Vlad Epurescu |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107233429/http://adevarul.ro/news/eveniment/ce-nu-s-a-vazut-televizor-timpul-protestelor-bucuresti-s-a-incercat-deturnarea-manifestatiei-miting-anti-iohannis-1_563a9ee2f5eaafab2c4fc96a/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。示威者要求提前选举<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34726826 |title=Romania: Protests despite Victor Ponta's resignation |work=BBC News |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107014714/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34726826 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和领导层全面改革<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gandul.info/politica/zeci-de-mii-de-romani-cer-in-strada-schimbarea-totala-a-clasei-politice-care-este-solutia-lui-iohannis-pentru-consultarile-de-la-cotroceni-14874328 |title=Zeci de mii de români cer în stradă SCHIMBAREA TOTALĂ a clasei politice. Care este SOLUŢIA lui IOHANNIS pentru consultările de la Cotroceni |work=Gândul |author=Clarice Dinu |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912060429/https://www.gandul.info/politica/consultari-la-cotroceni-iohannis-vorbim-despre-o-schimbare-de-paradigma-politica-psd-propune-o-noua-runda-de-discutii-pnl-ramane-la-anticipate-14874328 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。声援抗议在[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[巴黎|巴黎]]和[[马德里|马德里]]出现<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/incendiu-in-colectiv/manifestatiile-din-romania-sustinute-de-romanii-din-strainatate-nu-va-lasam-singuri-s-a-strigat-la-paris-si-londra.html |title=Manifestatiile din Romania, sustinute de romanii din strainatate. "Nu va lasam singuri", s-a strigat la Paris si Londra |work=Stirile Pro TV |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107213228/http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/incendiu-in-colectiv/manifestatiile-din-romania-sustinute-de-romanii-din-strainatate-nu-va-lasam-singuri-s-a-strigat-la-paris-si-londra.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
